.TH SENTINEL-TRAITS 1 "2026-03-08" "SENTINEL 0.1.0" "SENTINEL Manual"
.SH NAME
sentinel-traits \- list available persona trait dimensions and values
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B python3 list_traits.py
.RI [ OPTIONS ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Lists all persona trait dimensions and their allowed values. SENTINEL uses
a structured 6-dimension trait system for deterministic persona composition.
Each unique combination of traits produces a reproducible system prompt and
a SHA-256 trait fingerprint for auditing.
.PP
Dimensions: role (10 values), disposition (8), values (8),
stance_on_regulation (5), communication_style (6), conflict_approach (5).
Total unique combinations: 96,000.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BI \-d " DIM" "\fR,\fP \-\-dimension" " DIM"
Show only the specified dimension (e.g., "role", "disposition").
.SH EXAMPLES
List all dimensions and values:
.PP
.RS
python3 list_traits.py
.RE
.PP
List only role values:
.PP
.RS
python3 list_traits.py \-d role
.RE
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR sentinel-experiment (1),
.BR sentinel-fork (1)
